### get all roles
GET http://localhost:8000/api/roles

### Create a role
POST http://localhost:8000/api/roles
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Test",
  "permissions": [2, 4]
}

### Get role by ID
GET http://localhost:8000/api/roles/4

### Update a role
PUT http://localhost:8000/api/roles/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Admin",
  "permissions": [1]
}

### Delete a role
DELETE http://localhost:8000/api/roles/1